# docs.ampbox.io — Amplifier docs (PRIVATE to Ken).
# Copy to /mnt/services/docs.caddy and reload the edge Caddy.
# Thin reverse_proxy (same shape as wiki.caddy/muxterm.caddy). Upstream is
# oauth2-proxy (:4182), which enforces GitHub OAuth (kenotron-ms only) and
# shares the .ampbox.io SSO cookie, then proxies to the static docs (:8092).
# Do NOT point this straight at :8092 — that would be PUBLIC.
docs.ampbox.io {
	reverse_proxy http://127.0.0.1:4182
}
